description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a bit of an update on one gaming lawsuit I've been keeping my eyes on. Palworld is a game that's flown too far towards the copyrights of Nintendo and now are pressured to pay the price on a lawsuit that honestly could go anywhere. How? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Insane Palworld Nintendo Lawsuit Update...
